txt.en: 'Retreat! The tower falls! They have won, run for your lives!'
'Hold your ground maggots, and push these vermin out of my tower!'
'You think we're idiots, do you? Well I won't face you outside of my tower!'
'You've no strength in your arms, tender-morsel.'
'I'll feed your corpse to my Warg!'
'What's this!? The Free Peoples in my tower. Slaughter these curs and bring me their flesh!'
